{"tid":2188410,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現堂哥偷食應該點做？","createTime":"2020-09-04T08:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T15:53:39.000Z","uid":46869,"like":7,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"4570cfcbf5d5934f63405700227f30b712d71349","tid":2188410,"uid":46869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"話說我同堂哥不嬲由細到大感情好好，佢有賣啲靚生果，成日揸車拎啲比我地食，之後我落樓下拎。<br />\n<br />\n佢大我十年，結咗婚幾年，平時同佢老婆好恩愛。<br />\n<br />\n琴晚成十點幾佢又叫我落去攞哈密瓜，我上咗車唔夠5分鐘，有個女人上車，話係佢舊同學。之後我就落咗車。因為我同啊爺住得近，佢叫我順便拎埋去比啊爺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奇怪嘅事就發生，啱啱我媽同我講，堂哥老婆話佢琴晚成十二點先返屋企，話車埋我去啊爺屋企先返，所以晏咗。但明明琴日係我自己去，佢中間個段時間去咗邊無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成粒鐘，佢去咗邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後無岀聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb168e934cd6e69578bcc162b3b412cd94c51ef","tid":2188410,"uid":42402,"like":142,"dislike":0,"score":142,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"阿哥偷食唔洗你教"},{"pid":"160ca952c9226f6a742c33df36fe1d4dbc41364b","tid":2188410,"uid":76135,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"擺明想你知"},{"pid":"0ef4a975bcf681306495efcf5e7ba2c9a87efd28","tid":2188410,"uid":9392,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:29:14.000Z","msg":"快啲踢爆佢 搞撚到佢離婚 哈哈哈哈哈哈"},{"pid":"1bf77347d2d259c77c5826f21fbe7c9db7fdc7db","tid":2188410,"uid":170855,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"眼花姐 放左兩個哈密瓜係心口 就以為